<template>

          <v-list-group :value="true" no-action sub-group>

              <v-list-item-content>

              </v-list-item-content>

        </v-list-group>

export default {
  data: () => ({
    drawer: null,
    admins: [
        ['Management', 'mdi-account-multiple-outline'],
        ['Settings', 'mdi-cog-outline'],
      ],
      cruds: [
        ['Create', 'mdi-plus-outline'],
        ['Read', 'mdi-file-outline'],
        ['Update', 'mdi-update'],
        ['Delete', 'mdi-delete'],
      ],
    items: [
      {
        action: "mdi-view-dashboard",

        title: "標案",
      },
      {
        action: "mdi-book-account",
        active: true,
        items: [
          { title: "Breakfast & brunch" },
          { title: "New American" },
          { title: "Sushi" },
        ],
        title: "憑證",
      },
      {
        action: "mdi-account-settings",

        title: "設定",
      },

</script>
